# Commit Contract

Every production candidate must follow:

- One user-visible concern per commit.
- No bundled unrelated WIP.
- No commit may depend on untracked files.
- Clean worktree build must pass before deploy discussion.
- Exact files changed must be listed.
- Forbidden files must be confirmed untouched.
- Rollback command must be provided.
- Deploy only from clean main after approval.

If a commit mixes concerns, split it before production.
